Bu Pieck!


145
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:50,830
Unit Panzer!


146
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:53,700
Terima kasih sudah bekerja keras
bahkan hari ini!


147
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:56,660
Kamu juga, Bu Pieck.


148
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:58,540
Suasana hatimu baik hari ini?


149
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,790
Apa yang kau lakukan? Ayo.


150
00:10:01,330 --> 00:10:02,330
Ada apa?


151
